<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>HIPAA Compliance Monitoring — {{ practice_name }}</title>
<style>
@page {
    size: Letter landscape;
    margin: 0.5in;
    @bottom-center {
        content: "Issued by {{ presenter_brand }}.  Verify: {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}.  Valid until {{ valid_until_human }}.";
        font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
        font-size: 9pt;
        color: #666;
    }
}
body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-size: 11pt;
    margin: 0;
}
.frame {
    border: 6px double #14A89E;
    padding: 28px 36px 22px 36px;
    height: 7.0in;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}
.banner {
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #14A89E;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.banner .eyebrow {
    font-size: 10pt;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #14A89E;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}
.banner h1 {
    font-size: 32pt;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}
.banner .subtitle {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
}
.body-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    flex: 1;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-top: 4px;
}
.left-col {
    flex: 1.4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}
.right-col {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
}
.practice-name {
    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 36pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
}
.period {
    font-size: 12pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0 0 18px 0;
}
.statement {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
}
.summary-block {
    margin: 6px 0 0 0;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #f0fdfa;
    border-left: 4px solid #14A89E;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.summary-block .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a365d;
}
.signoff {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.signoff .role-line {
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
}
.attestation-card {
    background: #f7fafc;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
    border-left: 4px solid #14A89E;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.attestation-card .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a365d;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.attestation-card .hash {
    font-family: 'Courier New', 'Menlo', monospace;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    word-break: break-all;
    line-height: 1.35;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-top: 4px;
}
.attestation-card .verify-line {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.issuance-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #4a5568;
}
.issuance-card p {
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
}
.issuance-card .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.disclaimer {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.4;
}
.disclaimer p { margin: 0 0 4px 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="frame">

    <div class="banner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Wall Certificate</p>
        <h1>HIPAA Compliance Monitoring in Effect</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Cryptographically signed substrate — independently verifiable</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body-row">

        <div class="left-col">
            <p class="practice-name">{{ practice_name }}</p>
            <p class="period">For the period {{ period_start_human }} through {{ period_end_human }}</p>

            <p class="statement">
                The technical safeguards of <strong>{{ practice_name }}</strong> are monitored on a continuous automated schedule against a defined subset of 45 CFR §164.312 technical safeguards and the §164.308(a)(1)(ii)(D) information-system-activity-review control. Cryptographically signed evidence is captured by the {{ presenter_brand }} compliance substrate.
            </p>

            <div class="summary-block">
                <span class="label">Coverage:</span>
                {{ sites_covered_count }} site{{ 's' if sites_covered_count != 1 else '' }},
                {{ appliances_count }} compliance appliance{{ 's' if appliances_count != 1 else '' }},
                {{ workstations_count }} workstation{{ 's' if workstations_count != 1 else '' }}<br>
                <span class="label">Evidence:</span>
                {{ bundle_count }} signed bundle{{ 's' if bundle_count != 1 else '' }}
                · {{ ots_anchored_pct_str }}% Bitcoin-anchored
            </div>

            <div class="signoff">
                <p class="role-line">Reviewed by <strong>{{ privacy_officer_name }}</strong>, {{ privacy_officer_title }} (Designated Privacy Officer).</p>
                <p class="role-line">Issued under BAA dated {{ baa_dated_at_human }} with {{ baa_practice_name }}.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="right-col">

            <div class="attestation-card">
                <span class="label">Attestation Hash (SHA-256, Ed25519-signed)</span>
                <div class="hash">{{ attestation_hash }}</div>
                <p class="verify-line">
                    <strong>Verify:</strong><br>
                    Phone: {{ verify_phone }}<br>
                    Web: {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="issuance-card">
                <p><span class="label">Issued by:</span> {{ presenter_brand }}{{ presenter_contact_line }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Issuance:</span> {{ issued_at_human }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Valid until:</span> {{ valid_until_human }} (90 days)</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="disclaimer">
        <p>This letter is audit-supportive technical evidence. It contains no patient-identifying information and is not part of any designated record set under §164.524. It is not a substitute for the practice's §164.528 disclosure accounting, designated record set, §164.530(d) complaint log, or workforce sanction records. Auditors and carriers may request the Evidence Kit (cryptographically signed bundles + chain + OpenTimestamps anchors) for offline verification. To report a concern, contact compliance@osiriscare.com (best-effort acknowledgment within 7 business days; substantive response within 30 days) or the HHS Office for Civil Rights at hhs.gov/ocr/complaints.</p>
        <p>This wall certificate is an alternate display of the underlying Compliance Attestation Letter; the same Ed25519-signed payload backs both. Attestation-hash verification is supported through the term of the {{ presenter_brand }}–{{ baa_practice_name }} relationship plus a commercially reasonable wind-down period; the practice retains independent copies for §164.530(j) compliance.</p>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
